Hello... It's hot, isn't it? Can I use the bonfire? It's
really hot though...

The boss here has high attack power, so it's important to
strengthen your defense. It's also crucial to exploit its
weaknesses as you go along.

When it's hot, it's time for a bonfire...!! My stamina has
fully recovered!

Okay, you passed~ You guys are on fire~ Seriously, the
vibes are rising~
\SE[28] (Hmm... This spirit's energy is quite unique...)

Alright, from today we're gonna be Mabu I'll give you my
power right away! Step forward! Vega-chan
Hmm! Feels good~ Just don't move for a moment, okay...

Wow This Cheki is super cute~ Let's exchange Line with our
boyfriends~
Sigh... I got it... I'll bestow upon you my power...

By the way, why is Vega-chan using a gun? Fire and
lightning, which are her specialties, don't really go well
together. If she makes a little mistake, she might end up
catching fire~
Huh... What was that just now...?

\SE[20]It's none of your business. If you're not going to
stop using it, then I don't need it. \SE[19]I don't need
that kind of power, so you can keep it to yourself.
I-I didn't say that~ I was just asking~

Look, it's a Mabu... I'll give it to you, Vega- chan Come
back Okay

\SE[19]... There won't be a next time. If you keep making me
wait, I'll really leave.

It's a Mabu, so I know that much~ Alright then... Just a
little... Don't move... Teehee
Vega learned the secret technique \i[70]Cold Fusion!

\SE[94]Huh...? Is it okay? \!\SE[91]Even if I receive
something like this...

It's all for none other than Vega-chan~ Maybe I should lend
a hand too~?

\SE[90]This troublesome person over here has become
energetic...

This is the end of our trial If you feel like it, come and
play again sometime~
\SE[58]Sure, sure... If I feel like it...
